<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>yòng xiàng shén líng gē chàng 迦南182</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 qīng chén de shí hòu wǒ de líng zǎo zǎo sū xǐng, dàn qǐ liù xián qín zàn měi zhǔ.
 gē shēng piāo chū chuāng kǒu piāo xiàng yuǎn fāng. suí fēng yōu yōu huí dàng,
 bàn zhe niǎo yǔ bàn zhe huā xiāng, hé liú shān chuān yě yī tóng gē chàng,
 rén shēng duō měi hǎo yǒu yé sū zài shēn shàng, wǒ de xīn a duō me huān chàng
 wǒ de líng sū xǐng dàn qín gē yōu yáng,
 měi hǎo de shí guāng xiàn gěi zhǔ. wǒ de líng a gē chàng zài gē chàng.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>182</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>